+          summary: "Retention-guard quarantine events detected"
+          description: "One or more sid were quarantined because replay checkpoints fell behind Redis stream retention."
diff -ruN p33ops/runbooks/P33_AUTONOMY_REPLAY.md p33auto/runbooks/P33_AUTONOMY_REPLAY.md
